ISLAMABAD, Jun 03 (APP):Islamabad Electric Supply Company (IESCO) on Monday issued 3-day power suspension programme for Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday for various areas of its region due to necessary maintenance and routine development work.
According to IESCO Spokesman, the power supply of different feeders and grid stations would remain suspended for the period on Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday From 07:30 AM to 16:30 PM, Islamabad Circle, USA-I, USA-II & USA-III Feeders, and surrounding areas.
